{"tid":2413937,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男生「大三罷」藏萬用刀罪成 還押3周後今被判處240小時社會服務令","createTime":"2021-02-19T05:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T10:24:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3d3ffa0619e3c6b31f7fabe8d67a2ca67aeffa0d","tid":2413937,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:16:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13764\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13764&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69LTyP%2F9hhZoMZuVNmYF6dao%3D&h=a8363311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13764</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第八庭<br />\n#張志偉裁判官 #判刑<br />\n👤周(17) #1111鰂魚涌 🛑已還押21天<br />\n #管有工具作非法用途<br />\n<br />\n控罪1：管有適合作非法用途的工具並意圖作非法用途使用<br />\n被告被控於2019年11月11日，在鰂魚涌康怡廣場北座外管有1把可摺軍刀。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n以下是判刑結果：<br />\n法庭判處被告240小時社會服務令"},{"pid":"0b96992e0f15b1c35cc3b9b8b80e7bbdfa5cbca4","tid":2413937,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:18:04.000Z","msg":"肯定又覆核<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1935c365e0bf795d19b95d9de2e05e5302be718","tid":2413937,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:24:44.000Z","msg":"良心法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b59b0c03398d9344fd726ec1d39b05d1a03507","tid":2413937,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b96992e0f15b1c35cc3b9b8b80e7bbdfa5cbca4","tid":2413937,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:18:04.000Z","msg":"肯定又覆核<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:26:22.000Z","msg":"到時唔知要坐幾耐"},{"pid":"071ffd415bb3eeef53b2208be113aa8bff19a299","tid":2413937,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a2525069b2dc834efc97d77f327149d3564a09","tid":2413937,"uid":138964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:53:18.000Z","msg":"一把萬用刀 還柙完都 做要爆240<br />\n何其重判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a5d43cde734500be9367c2ee5e096c6efd7d51","tid":2413937,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:56:04.000Z","msg":"兩名中學男生前年11月大三罷首天，在鰂魚涌康怡廣場外遭警員搜出萬用刀及螺旋鉗等物品。案件經審訊後，其中一名男生脫罪，惟裁判官張志偉認為另一名自辯時力證萬用刀合法用途的童軍領袖並非誠實可靠，裁定他罪成，案件今日判刑。張官指萬用刀的破壞力不大，法庭因應不同類別的工具，應有不同判刑結果，接納被告受社會氛圍影響，犯案只是個別事件，最終判男生接受社會服務令240小時。庭上不少親友聞判後喜極而泣，散庭時被告父母不禁激動相擁。<br />\n<br />\n辯方今求情時透露，被告已入讀電影系，參舆電影製作是他長久以來的夢想，若被判處拘押式刑罰，未必能夠繼續學業。辯方更引述前無綫電視主持人李有毅的求情信，指被告勤奮及有親和力。<br />\n<br />\n辯方引述被告父母求情信指，被告還柙期間意志消沉、食不下嚥，強調被告對犯案深感悔懊，已得到充足教訓。辯方強調，被告身藏常見的萬用刀，而非較嚴重的物件如炸彈燃料，相信三星期還柙已足以帶出阻嚇性，建議法庭按報告建議判處社會服務令，給予被告一次機會。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官張志偉判刑時指，本案重點並非被告身藏萬用刀，而是他在警誡下承認參與堵路。張官續指，萬用刀相比其他工具而言，破壞力不算大，認為法庭針對不同類別的工具，應有不同判刑結果。張官再指，報告顯示被告對案件已有反省，接納被告受社會氛圍影響，犯案只是個別事件，希望被告在造成破壞後能夠回饋社會，最後判處他接受240小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210219/D35XOXEFAVDAPKZNMGVIUPD5SM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210219%2FD35XOXEFAVDAPKZNMGVIUPD5SM%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69LTyP%2F9hhZoMZuVNmYF6dao%3D&h=3c2c6cbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210219%2FD35XOXEFAVDAPKZNMGVIUPD5SM%2F&h=a170c847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210219/D35XOXEFAVDAPKZNMGVIUPD5SM/</a>"},{"pid":"64969a0cf486894b95a934db2459e070cfc98bba","tid":2413937,"uid":44646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a9a2525069b2dc834efc97d77f327149d3564a09","tid":2413937,"uid":138964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:53:18.000Z","msg":"一把萬用刀 還柙完都 做要爆240<br />\n何其重判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:01:20.000Z","msg":"大陸仔持刀恐嚇同學就唔告"},{"pid":"72e026ecfda15319ca2acc101ca482cb9badf765","tid":2413937,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:04:35.000Z","msg":"肥張都幾兩極"},{"pid":"80598103beaa9402dcea17738769a28363a3b0c9","tid":2413937,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9672b172e40d701182be000b810531583977c3c","tid":2413937,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:14:51.000Z","msg":"裁判官張志偉判刑時指，本案重點並非被告身藏萬用刀<br />\n<br />\n個控罪就係告手足藏刀做「非法用途」，點會唔係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee874b5c08384c0c9d082c7b319339901d65d2a","tid":2413937,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:14:50.000Z","msg":"萬用刀都唔得<br />\n有病？？"},{"pid":"2d8bbdb02f1b61042adedc9786a2615ac44d0481","tid":2413937,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:19:06.000Z","msg":"裁判官張志偉判刑時指，被告已經被還押三星期，相信他已經得到深刻教訓，重犯機會低。裁判官又指，當日被告藏有的摺刀不屬於大型工具，不會造成大型破壞，接納被告受社會氛圍影響，相信本案屬個別事件，最終判被告240小時社會服務令。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/11-11-%E4%B8%89%E7%BD%B7-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E8%97%8F%E8%90%AC%E7%94%A8%E5%88%80%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC-%E5%AE%98%E5%88%A4-240-%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%8D%E4%BB%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F11-11-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25BD%25B7-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%2597%258F%25E8%2590%